{21010}{}{Hero. She called me a hero.}
{22000}{}{[We both know that there are no heroes. Just dead memories, and more blood to fill up all the emptiness. So much for all that light in the darkness crap]}
{22010}{}{How the fuck do I get out of this one alive?}
